metadata.name: Ram1 // NeoTokyo ShowDown
metadata.description:
Ram 1 // NeoTokyo ShowDown is based on a Random reminiscence file depicting a well known Duo biker gang in the streets of Neo Tokyo  in late AD 2019.

 Some half corrupted data log files may indicate their implication in the electro /  synthwave music scene from that era too.

RAM ( Retro Alternate Memories ) is a series that evolves around a unique and altered memories of several popular narratives where everything has slightly shifted or completely transformed into a unique and unprecedented reminiscence.

Original reminiscence resolution . Size : 6000 x 3375
